videos.headline: Adkins swings pass to Huntley for 51-yard TD
videos.description: Aggies' Josh Adkins throws a swing pass to Jason Huntley who bursts for a 51-yard touchdown to cut the Ragin' Cajuns' lead to 14-7.

videos.headline: Huntley scores 87-yard TD on kickoff return
videos.description: On a kickoff return, Jason Huntley catches and runs 87 yards for a touchdown to cut the Aggies' deficit to 21-14.

videos.headline: Mitchell bursts for 36-yard TD
videos.description: Ragin' Cajuns' Elijah  Mitchell finds a hole and bursts for a 36-yard touchdown to lock up the game with a 59-38 lead early in the 4th.
